    <title>在執行sudo npm install 時，出現 permission denied, mkdir &quot;xxx&quot; 權限錯誤</title>
    <link href="http://antfire70007.github.io/2017/11/30/problem-with-npm-install/"/>
    <id>http://antfire70007.github.io/2017/11/30/problem-with-npm-install/</id>
    <published>2017-11-30T14:34:39.552Z</published>
    <updated>2017-11-25T14:13:40.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="問題描述"><a href="#問題描述" class="headerlink" title="問題描述"></a>問題描述</h1><p>在執行sudo npm install時，遇到以下錯誤<br><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gyp verb build dir attempting to create <span class="string">"build"</span> dir: ...</span><br><span class="line">gyp ERR! configure error</span><br><span class="line">gyp ERR! stack Error: EACCES: permission denied, mkdir <span class="string">'...'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>即使我下了sudo 依然如故，疑似是安裝過程中，執行了需要授權的指令 例如 <code>mkdir</code>等</p><h1 id="解決方法"><a href="#解決方法" class="headerlink" title="解決方法"></a>解決方法</h1><p>在<code>sudo npm install</code> 後面加上權限相關參數 <code>--unsafe-perm=true --allow-root</code><br>在過程中可能會需要貴方手動輸入 <code>agree</code></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo npm install --unsafe-perm=<span class="literal">true</span> --allow-root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>tada~~</p><h1 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h1><p><a href="https://github.com/npm/npm/issues/17268" target="_blank" rel="noopener">stackoverflow</a></p>]]></content>
    
